39template <typename T>
40void SerializeColor(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const Color<T> &color)
41{
42 bos->writeInt(color.red);
43 bos->writeInt(color.green);
44 bos->writeInt(color.blue);
45 bos->writeInt(color.alpha);
46}
47
48template <class ObjectType>
49void SerializeOffsetBindingPointerVector(
50 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
51 const std::vector<gl::OffsetBindingPointer<ObjectType>> &offsetBindingPointerVector)
52{
53 for (size_t i = 0; i < offsetBindingPointerVector.size(); i++)
54 {
55 bos->writeInt(offsetBindingPointerVector[i].id().value);
56 bos->writeInt(offsetBindingPointerVector[i].getOffset());
57 bos->writeInt(offsetBindingPointerVector[i].getSize());
58 }
59}
60
61template <class ObjectType>
62void SerializeBindingPointerVector(
63 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
64 const std::vector<gl::BindingPointer<ObjectType>> &bindingPointerVector)
65{
66 for (size_t i = 0; i < bindingPointerVector.size(); i++)
67 {
68 bos->writeInt(bindingPointerVector[i].id().value);
69 }
70}

72template <class T>
73void SerializeRange(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::Range<T> &range)
74{
75 bos->writeInt(range.low());
76 bos->writeInt(range.high());
77}
78
79bool IsValidColorAttachmentBinding(GLenum binding, size_t colorAttachmentsCount)
80{
81 return binding == GL_BACK || (binding >= GL_COLOR_ATTACHMENT0 &&
82 (binding - GL_COLOR_ATTACHMENT0) < colorAttachmentsCount);
83}
84
85Result ReadPixelsFromAttachment(const gl::Context *context,
86 gl::Framebuffer *framebuffer,
87 const gl::FramebufferAttachment &framebufferAttachment,
88 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
89 MemoryBuffer **pixels)
90{
91 gl::Extents extents = framebufferAttachment.getSize();
92 GLenum binding = framebufferAttachment.getBinding();
93 gl::InternalFormat format = *framebufferAttachment.getFormat().info;
94 if (IsValidColorAttachmentBinding(binding,
95 framebuffer->getState().getColorAttachments().size()))
96 {
97 format = framebuffer->getImplementation()->getImplementationColorReadFormat(context);
98 }
99 ANGLE_CHECK_GL_ALLOC(const_cast<gl::Context *>(context),
100 scratchBuffer->getInitialized(
101 format.pixelBytes * extents.width * extents.height, pixels, 0));
102 ANGLE_TRY(framebuffer->readPixels(context, gl::Rectangle{0, 0, extents.width, extents.height},
103 format.format, format.type, gl::PixelPackState{}, nullptr,
104 (*pixels)->data()));
105 return Result::Continue;
106}
107void SerializeImageIndex(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::ImageIndex &imageIndex)
108{
109 bos->writeEnum(imageIndex.getType());
110 bos->writeInt(imageIndex.getLevelIndex());
111 bos->writeInt(imageIndex.getLayerIndex());
112 bos->writeInt(imageIndex.getLayerCount());
113}

115Result SerializeFramebufferAttachment(const gl::Context *context,
116 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
117 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
118 gl::Framebuffer *framebuffer,
119 const gl::FramebufferAttachment &framebufferAttachment)
120{
121 if (framebufferAttachment.type() == GL_TEXTURE ||
122 framebufferAttachment.type() == GL_RENDERBUFFER)
123 {
124 bos->writeInt(framebufferAttachment.id());
125 }
126 bos->writeInt(framebufferAttachment.type());
127 // serialize target variable
128 bos->writeInt(framebufferAttachment.getBinding());
129 if (framebufferAttachment.type() == GL_TEXTURE)
130 {
131 SerializeImageIndex(bos, framebufferAttachment.getTextureImageIndex());
132 }
133 bos->writeInt(framebufferAttachment.getNumViews());
134 bos->writeBool(framebufferAttachment.isMultiview());
135 bos->writeInt(framebufferAttachment.getBaseViewIndex());
136 bos->writeInt(framebufferAttachment.getRenderToTextureSamples());
137
138 if (framebufferAttachment.type() != GL_TEXTURE &&
139 framebufferAttachment.type() != GL_RENDERBUFFER)
140 {
141 GLenum prevReadBufferState = framebuffer->getReadBufferState();
142 GLenum binding = framebufferAttachment.getBinding();
143 if (IsValidColorAttachmentBinding(binding,
144 framebuffer->getState().getColorAttachments().size()))
145 {
146 framebuffer->setReadBuffer(framebufferAttachment.getBinding());
147 ANGLE_TRY(framebuffer->syncState(context, GL_FRAMEBUFFER, gl::Command::Other));
148 }
149 MemoryBuffer *pixelsPtr = nullptr;
150 ANGLE_TRY(ReadPixelsFromAttachment(context, framebuffer, framebufferAttachment,
151 scratchBuffer, &pixelsPtr));
152 bos->writeBytes(pixelsPtr->data(), pixelsPtr->size());
153 // Reset framebuffer state
154 framebuffer->setReadBuffer(prevReadBufferState);
155 }
156 return Result::Continue;
157}
158
159Result SerializeFramebufferState(const gl::Context *context,
160 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
161 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
162 gl::Framebuffer *framebuffer,
163 const gl::FramebufferState &framebufferState)
164{
165 bos->writeInt(framebufferState.id().value);
166 bos->writeString(framebufferState.getLabel());
167 bos->writeIntVector(framebufferState.getDrawBufferStates());
168 bos->writeInt(framebufferState.getReadBufferState());
169 bos->writeInt(framebufferState.getDefaultWidth());
170 bos->writeInt(framebufferState.getDefaultHeight());
171 bos->writeInt(framebufferState.getDefaultSamples());
172 bos->writeBool(framebufferState.getDefaultFixedSampleLocations());
173 bos->writeInt(framebufferState.getDefaultLayers());
174
175 const std::vector<gl::FramebufferAttachment> &colorAttachments =
176 framebufferState.getColorAttachments();
177 for (const gl::FramebufferAttachment &colorAttachment : colorAttachments)
178 {
179 if (colorAttachment.isAttached())
180 {
181 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeFramebufferAttachment(context, bos, scratchBuffer, framebuffer,
182 colorAttachment));
183 }
184 }
185 if (framebuffer->getDepthStencilAttachment())
186 {
187 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeFramebufferAttachment(context, bos, scratchBuffer, framebuffer,
188 *framebuffer->getDepthStencilAttachment()));
189 }
190 else
191 {
192 if (framebuffer->getDepthAttachment())
193 {
194 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeFramebufferAttachment(context, bos, scratchBuffer, framebuffer,
195 *framebuffer->getDepthAttachment()));
196 }
197 if (framebuffer->getStencilAttachment())
198 {
199 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeFramebufferAttachment(context, bos, scratchBuffer, framebuffer,
200 *framebuffer->getStencilAttachment()));
201 }
202 }
203 return Result::Continue;
204}

206Result SerializeFramebuffer(const gl::Context *context,
207 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
208 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
209 gl::Framebuffer *framebuffer)
210{
211 return SerializeFramebufferState(context, bos, scratchBuffer, framebuffer,
212 framebuffer->getState());

215void SerializeRasterizerState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
216 const gl::RasterizerState &rasterizerState)
217{
218 bos->writeBool(rasterizerState.cullFace);
219 bos->writeEnum(rasterizerState.cullMode);
220 bos->writeInt(rasterizerState.frontFace);
221 bos->writeBool(rasterizerState.polygonOffsetFill);
222 bos->writeInt(rasterizerState.polygonOffsetFactor);
223 bos->writeInt(rasterizerState.polygonOffsetUnits);
224 bos->writeBool(rasterizerState.pointDrawMode);
225 bos->writeBool(rasterizerState.multiSample);
226 bos->writeBool(rasterizerState.rasterizerDiscard);
227 bos->writeBool(rasterizerState.dither);
228}

271void SerializeVertexAttribCurrentValueData(
272 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
273 const gl::VertexAttribCurrentValueData &vertexAttribCurrentValueData)
274{
275 ASSERT(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Type == gl::VertexAttribType::Float ||
276 vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Type == gl::VertexAttribType::Int ||
277 vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Type == gl::VertexAttribType::UnsignedInt);
278 if (vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Type == gl::VertexAttribType::Float)
279 {
280 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.FloatValues[0]);
281 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.FloatValues[1]);
282 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.FloatValues[2]);
283 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.FloatValues[3]);
284 }
285 else if (vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Type == gl::VertexAttribType::Int)
286 {
287 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.IntValues[0]);
288 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.IntValues[1]);
289 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.IntValues[2]);
290 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.IntValues[3]);
291 }
292 else
293 {
294 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.UnsignedIntValues[0]);
295 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.UnsignedIntValues[1]);
296 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.UnsignedIntValues[2]);
297 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribCurrentValueData.Values.UnsignedIntValues[3]);
298 }
299}

333void SerializeGLContextStates(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::State &state)
334{
335 bos->writeInt(state.getClientType());
336 bos->writeInt(state.getContextPriority());
337 bos->writeInt(state.getClientMajorVersion());
338 bos->writeInt(state.getClientMinorVersion());
339
340 SerializeColor(bos, state.getColorClearValue());
341 bos->writeInt(state.getDepthClearValue());
342 bos->writeInt(state.getStencilClearValue());
343 SerializeRasterizerState(bos, state.getRasterizerState());
344 bos->writeBool(state.isScissorTestEnabled());
345 SerializeRectangle(bos, state.getScissor());
346 SerializeBlendStateExt(bos, state.getBlendStateExt());
347 SerializeColor(bos, state.getBlendColor());
348 bos->writeBool(state.isSampleAlphaToCoverageEnabled());
349 bos->writeBool(state.isSampleCoverageEnabled());
350 bos->writeInt(state.getSampleCoverageValue());
351 bos->writeBool(state.getSampleCoverageInvert());
352 bos->writeBool(state.isSampleMaskEnabled());
353 bos->writeInt(state.getMaxSampleMaskWords());
354 const auto &sampleMaskValues = state.getSampleMaskValues();
355 for (size_t i = 0; i < sampleMaskValues.size(); i++)
356 {
357 bos->writeInt(sampleMaskValues[i]);
358 }
359 SerializeDepthStencilState(bos, state.getDepthStencilState());
360 bos->writeInt(state.getStencilRef());
361 bos->writeInt(state.getStencilBackRef());
362 bos->writeInt(state.getLineWidth());
363 bos->writeInt(state.getGenerateMipmapHint());
364 bos->writeInt(state.getTextureFilteringHint());
365 bos->writeInt(state.getFragmentShaderDerivativeHint());
366 bos->writeBool(state.isBindGeneratesResourceEnabled());
367 bos->writeBool(state.areClientArraysEnabled());
368 SerializeRectangle(bos, state.getViewport());
369 bos->writeInt(state.getNearPlane());
370 bos->writeInt(state.getFarPlane());
371 if (state.getReadFramebuffer())
372 {
373 bos->writeInt(state.getReadFramebuffer()->id().value);
374 }
375 if (state.getDrawFramebuffer())
376 {
377 bos->writeInt(state.getDrawFramebuffer()->id().value);
378 }
379 bos->writeInt(state.getRenderbufferId().value);
380 if (state.getProgram())
381 {
382 bos->writeInt(state.getProgram()->id().value);
383 }
384 if (state.getProgramPipeline())
385 {
386 bos->writeInt(state.getProgramPipeline()->id().value);
387 }
388 bos->writeEnum(state.getProvokingVertex());
389 const std::vector<gl::VertexAttribCurrentValueData> &vertexAttribCurrentValues =
390 state.getVertexAttribCurrentValues();
391 for (size_t i = 0; i < vertexAttribCurrentValues.size(); i++)
392 {
393 SerializeVertexAttribCurrentValueData(bos, vertexAttribCurrentValues[i]);
394 }
395 if (state.getVertexArray())
396 {
397 bos->writeInt(state.getVertexArray()->id().value);
398 }
399 bos->writeInt(state.getCurrentValuesTypeMask().to_ulong());
400 bos->writeInt(state.getActiveSampler());
401 for (const auto &textures : state.getBoundTexturesForCapture())
402 {
403 SerializeBindingPointerVector<gl::Texture>(bos, textures);
404 }
405 bos->writeInt(state.getTexturesIncompatibleWithSamplers().to_ulong());
406 SerializeBindingPointerVector<gl::Sampler>(bos, state.getSamplers());
407 for (const gl::ImageUnit &imageUnit : state.getImageUnits())
408 {
409 SerializeImageUnit(bos, imageUnit);
410 }
411 for (const auto &query : state.getActiveQueriesForCapture())
412 {
413 bos->writeInt(query.id().value);
414 }
415 for (const auto &boundBuffer : state.getBoundBuffersForCapture())
416 {
417 bos->writeInt(boundBuffer.id().value);
418 }
419 SerializeOffsetBindingPointerVector<gl::Buffer>(bos,
420 state.getOffsetBindingPointerUniformBuffers());
421 SerializeOffsetBindingPointerVector<gl::Buffer>(
422 bos, state.getOffsetBindingPointerAtomicCounterBuffers());
423 SerializeOffsetBindingPointerVector<gl::Buffer>(
424 bos, state.getOffsetBindingPointerShaderStorageBuffers());
425 if (state.getCurrentTransformFeedback())
426 {
427 bos->writeInt(state.getCurrentTransformFeedback()->id().value);
428 }
429 SerializePixelUnpackState(bos, state.getUnpackState());
430 SerializePixelPackState(bos, state.getPackState());
431 bos->writeBool(state.isPrimitiveRestartEnabled());
432 bos->writeBool(state.isMultisamplingEnabled());
433 bos->writeBool(state.isSampleAlphaToOneEnabled());
434 bos->writeInt(state.getCoverageModulation());
435 bos->writeBool(state.getFramebufferSRGB());
436 bos->writeBool(state.isRobustResourceInitEnabled());
437 bos->writeBool(state.isProgramBinaryCacheEnabled());
438 bos->writeBool(state.isTextureRectangleEnabled());
439 bos->writeInt(state.getMaxShaderCompilerThreads());
440 bos->writeInt(state.getEnabledClipDistances().to_ulong());
441 bos->writeInt(state.getBlendFuncConstantAlphaDrawBuffers().to_ulong());
442 bos->writeInt(state.getBlendFuncConstantColorDrawBuffers().to_ulong());
443 bos->writeBool(state.noSimultaneousConstantColorAndAlphaBlendFunc());
444}

446void SerializeBufferState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::BufferState &bufferState)
447{
448 bos->writeString(bufferState.getLabel());
449 bos->writeEnum(bufferState.getUsage());
450 bos->writeInt(bufferState.getSize());
451 bos->writeInt(bufferState.getAccessFlags());
452 bos->writeInt(bufferState.getAccess());
453 bos->writeInt(bufferState.isMapped());
454 bos->writeInt(bufferState.getMapOffset());
455 bos->writeInt(bufferState.getMapLength());
456}
457
458Result SerializeBuffer(const gl::Context *context,
459 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
460 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
461 gl::Buffer *buffer)
462{
463 SerializeBufferState(bos, buffer->getState());
464 MemoryBuffer *dataPtr = nullptr;
465 ANGLE_CHECK_GL_ALLOC(
466 const_cast<gl::Context *>(context),
467 scratchBuffer->getInitialized(static_cast<size_t>(buffer->getSize()), &dataPtr, 0));
468 ANGLE_TRY(buffer->getSubData(context, 0, dataPtr->size(), dataPtr->data()));
469 bos->writeBytes(dataPtr->data(), dataPtr->size());
470 return Result::Continue;
471}
472void SerializeColorGeneric(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const ColorGeneric &colorGeneric)
473{
474 ASSERT(colorGeneric.type == ColorGeneric::Type::Float ||
475 colorGeneric.type == ColorGeneric::Type::Int ||
476 colorGeneric.type == ColorGeneric::Type::UInt);
477 bos->writeEnum(colorGeneric.type);
478 if (colorGeneric.type == ColorGeneric::Type::Float)
479 {
480 SerializeColor(bos, colorGeneric.colorF);
481 }
482 else if (colorGeneric.type == ColorGeneric::Type::Int)
483 {
484 SerializeColor(bos, colorGeneric.colorI);
485 }
486 else
487 {
488 SerializeColor(bos, colorGeneric.colorUI);
489 }
490}

492void SerializeSamplerState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::SamplerState &samplerState)
493{
494 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getMinFilter());
495 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getMagFilter());
496 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getWrapS());
497 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getWrapT());
498 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getWrapR());
499 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getMaxAnisotropy());
500 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getMinLod());
501 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getMaxLod());
502 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getCompareMode());
503 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getCompareFunc());
504 bos->writeInt(samplerState.getSRGBDecode());
505 SerializeColorGeneric(bos, samplerState.getBorderColor());
506}

548
549Result SerializeRenderbuffer(const gl::Context *context,
550 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
551 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
552 gl::Renderbuffer *renderbuffer)
553{
554 SerializeRenderbufferState(bos, renderbuffer->getState());
555 bos->writeString(renderbuffer->getLabel());
556 MemoryBuffer *pixelsPtr = nullptr;
557 ANGLE_CHECK_GL_ALLOC(
558 const_cast<gl::Context *>(context),
559 scratchBuffer->getInitialized(renderbuffer->getMemorySize(), &pixelsPtr, 0));
560 gl::PixelPackState packState;
561 packState.alignment = 1;
562 ANGLE_TRY(renderbuffer->getImplementation()->getRenderbufferImage(
563 context, packState, nullptr, renderbuffer->getImplementationColorReadFormat(context),
564 renderbuffer->getImplementationColorReadType(context), pixelsPtr->data()));
565 bos->writeBytes(pixelsPtr->data(), pixelsPtr->size());
566 return Result::Continue;
567}

576void SerializeShaderVariable(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const sh::ShaderVariable &shaderVariable)
577{
578 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.type);
579 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.precision);
580 bos->writeString(shaderVariable.name);
581 bos->writeString(shaderVariable.mappedName);
582 bos->writeIntVector(shaderVariable.arraySizes);
583 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.staticUse);
584 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.active);
585 for (const sh::ShaderVariable &field : shaderVariable.fields)
586 {
587 SerializeShaderVariable(bos, field);
588 }
589 bos->writeString(shaderVariable.structName);
590 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.isRowMajorLayout);
591 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.location);
592 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.binding);
593 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.imageUnitFormat);
594 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.offset);
595 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.readonly);
596 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.writeonly);
597 bos->writeInt(shaderVariable.index);
598 bos->writeEnum(shaderVariable.interpolation);
599 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.isInvariant);
600 bos->writeBool(shaderVariable.texelFetchStaticUse);
601}
602
603void SerializeShaderVariablesVector(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
604 const std::vector<sh::ShaderVariable> &shaderVariables)
605{
606 for (const sh::ShaderVariable &shaderVariable : shaderVariables)
607 {
608 SerializeShaderVariable(bos, shaderVariable);
609 }
610}

612void SerializeInterfaceBlocksVector(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
613 const std::vector<sh::InterfaceBlock> &interfaceBlocks)
614{
615 for (const sh::InterfaceBlock &interfaceBlock : interfaceBlocks)
616 {
617 bos->writeString(interfaceBlock.name);
618 bos->writeString(interfaceBlock.mappedName);
619 bos->writeString(interfaceBlock.instanceName);
620 bos->writeInt(interfaceBlock.arraySize);
621 bos->writeEnum(interfaceBlock.layout);
622 bos->writeInt(interfaceBlock.binding);
623 bos->writeBool(interfaceBlock.staticUse);
624 bos->writeBool(interfaceBlock.active);
625 bos->writeEnum(interfaceBlock.blockType);
626 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, interfaceBlock.fields);
627 }
628}
629
630void SerializeShaderState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::ShaderState &shaderState)
631{
632 bos->writeString(shaderState.getLabel());
633 bos->writeEnum(shaderState.getShaderType());
634 bos->writeInt(shaderState.getShaderVersion());
635 bos->writeString(shaderState.getTranslatedSource());
636 bos->writeString(shaderState.getSource());
637 SerializeWorkGroupSize(bos, shaderState.getLocalSize());
638 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, shaderState.getInputVaryings());
639 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, shaderState.getOutputVaryings());
640 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, shaderState.getUniforms());
641 SerializeInterfaceBlocksVector(bos, shaderState.getUniformBlocks());
642 SerializeInterfaceBlocksVector(bos, shaderState.getShaderStorageBlocks());
643 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, shaderState.getAllAttributes());
644 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, shaderState.getActiveAttributes());
645 SerializeShaderVariablesVector(bos, shaderState.getActiveOutputVariables());
646 bos->writeBool(shaderState.getEarlyFragmentTestsOptimization());
647 bos->writeInt(shaderState.getNumViews());
648 if (shaderState.getGeometryShaderInputPrimitiveType().valid())
649 {
650 bos->writeEnum(shaderState.getGeometryShaderInputPrimitiveType().value());
651 }
652 if (shaderState.getGeometryShaderOutputPrimitiveType().valid())
653 {
654 bos->writeEnum(shaderState.getGeometryShaderOutputPrimitiveType().value());
655 }
656 if (shaderState.getGeometryShaderInvocations().valid())
657 {
658 bos->writeInt(shaderState.getGeometryShaderInvocations().value());
659 }
660 bos->writeEnum(shaderState.getCompileStatus());
661}

663void SerializeShader(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, gl::Shader *shader)
664{
665 SerializeShaderState(bos, shader->getState());
666 bos->writeInt(shader->getHandle().value);
667 bos->writeInt(shader->getRefCount());
668 bos->writeBool(shader->isFlaggedForDeletion());
669 // does not serialize mType because it is already serialized in SerializeShaderState
670 bos->writeString(shader->getInfoLogString());
671 bos->writeString(shader->getCompilerResourcesString());
672 bos->writeInt(shader->getCurrentMaxComputeWorkGroupInvocations());
673 bos->writeInt(shader->getMaxComputeSharedMemory());
674}

726void SerializeProgramState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::ProgramState &programState)
727{
728 bos->writeString(programState.getLabel());
729 SerializeWorkGroupSize(bos, programState.getComputeShaderLocalSize());
730 for (gl::Shader *shader : programState.getAttachedShaders())
731 {
732 if (shader)
733 {
734 bos->writeInt(shader->getHandle().value);
735 }
736 else
737 {
738 bos->writeInt(0);
739 }
740 }
741 for (bool isAttached : programState.getAttachedShadersMarkedForDetach())
742 {
743 bos->writeBool(isAttached);
744 }
745 bos->writeInt(programState.getLocationsUsedForXfbExtension());
746 for (const std::string &transformFeedbackVaryingName :
747 programState.getTransformFeedbackVaryingNames())
748 {
749 bos->writeString(transformFeedbackVaryingName);
750 }
751 bos->writeInt(programState.getActiveUniformBlockBindingsMask().to_ulong());
752 SerializeVariableLocationsVector(bos, programState.getUniformLocations());
753 SerializeBufferVariablesVector(bos, programState.getBufferVariables());
754 SerializeRange(bos, programState.getAtomicCounterUniformRange());
755 SerializeVariableLocationsVector(bos, programState.getSecondaryOutputLocations());
756 bos->writeInt(programState.getActiveOutputVariables().to_ulong());
757 for (GLenum outputVariableType : programState.getOutputVariableTypes())
758 {
759 bos->writeInt(outputVariableType);
760 }
761 bos->writeInt(programState.getDrawBufferTypeMask().to_ulong());
762 bos->writeBool(programState.hasBinaryRetrieveableHint());
763 bos->writeBool(programState.isSeparable());
764 bos->writeBool(programState.hasEarlyFragmentTestsOptimization());
765 bos->writeInt(programState.getNumViews());
766 bos->writeEnum(programState.getGeometryShaderInputPrimitiveType());
767 bos->writeEnum(programState.getGeometryShaderOutputPrimitiveType());
768 bos->writeInt(programState.getGeometryShaderInvocations());
769 bos->writeInt(programState.getGeometryShaderMaxVertices());
770 bos->writeInt(programState.getDrawIDLocation());
771 bos->writeInt(programState.getBaseVertexLocation());
772 bos->writeInt(programState.getBaseInstanceLocation());
773 SerializeProgramAliasedBindings(bos, programState.getUniformLocationBindings());
774}

776void SerializeProgramBindings(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
777 const gl::ProgramBindings &programBindings)
778{
779 for (const auto &programBinding : programBindings)
780 {
781 bos->writeString(programBinding.first);
782 bos->writeInt(programBinding.second);
783 }
784}

786void SerializeProgram(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, gl::Program *program)
787{
788 SerializeProgramState(bos, program->getState());
789 bos->writeBool(program->isValidated());
790 SerializeProgramBindings(bos, program->getAttributeBindings());
791 SerializeProgramAliasedBindings(bos, program->getFragmentOutputLocations());
792 SerializeProgramAliasedBindings(bos, program->getFragmentOutputIndexes());
793 bos->writeBool(program->isLinked());
794 bos->writeBool(program->isFlaggedForDeletion());
795 bos->writeInt(program->getRefCount());
796 bos->writeInt(program->id().value);
797}

799void SerializeImageDesc(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::ImageDesc &imageDesc)
800{
801 SerializeExtents(bos, imageDesc.size);
802 SerializeFormat(bos, imageDesc.format);

808void SerializeTextureState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::TextureState &textureState)
809{
810 bos->writeEnum(textureState.getType());
811 SerializeSwizzleState(bos, textureState.getSwizzleState());
812 SerializeSamplerState(bos, textureState.getSamplerState());
813 bos->writeEnum(textureState.getSRGBOverride());
814 bos->writeInt(textureState.getBaseLevel());
815 bos->writeInt(textureState.getMaxLevel());
816 bos->writeInt(textureState.getDepthStencilTextureMode());
817 bos->writeBool(textureState.hasBeenBoundAsImage());
818 bos->writeBool(textureState.getImmutableFormat());
819 bos->writeInt(textureState.getImmutableLevels());
820 bos->writeInt(textureState.getUsage());
821 const std::vector<gl::ImageDesc> &imageDescs = textureState.getImageDescs();
822 for (const gl::ImageDesc &imageDesc : imageDescs)
823 {
824 SerializeImageDesc(bos, imageDesc);
825 }
826 SerializeRectangle(bos, textureState.getCrop());
827
828 bos->writeInt(textureState.getGenerateMipmapHint());
829 bos->writeEnum(textureState.getInitState());
830}
831
832Result SerializeTextureData(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
833 const gl::Context *context,
834 gl::Texture *texture,
835 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer)
836{
837 gl::ImageIndexIterator imageIter = gl::ImageIndexIterator::MakeGeneric(
838 texture->getType(), 0, texture->getMipmapMaxLevel() + 1, gl::ImageIndex::kEntireLevel,
839 gl::ImageIndex::kEntireLevel);
840 while (imageIter.hasNext())
841 {
842 gl::ImageIndex index = imageIter.next();
843
844 const gl::ImageDesc &desc = texture->getTextureState().getImageDesc(index);
845
846 if (desc.size.empty())
847 continue;
848
849 const gl::InternalFormat &format = *desc.format.info;
850
851 // Check for supported textures
852 ASSERT(index.getType() == gl::TextureType::_2D || index.getType() == gl::TextureType::_3D ||
853 index.getType() == gl::TextureType::_2DArray ||
854 index.getType() == gl::TextureType::CubeMap);
855
856 GLenum getFormat = format.format;
857 GLenum getType = format.type;
858
859 const gl::Extents size(desc.size.width, desc.size.height, desc.size.depth);
860 const gl::PixelUnpackState &unpack = context->getState().getUnpackState();
861
862 GLuint endByte = 0;
863 bool unpackSize = format.computePackUnpackEndByte(getType, size, unpack, true, &endByte);
864 ASSERT(unpackSize);
865 MemoryBuffer *texelsPtr = nullptr;
866 ANGLE_CHECK_GL_ALLOC(const_cast<gl::Context *>(context),
867 scratchBuffer->getInitialized(endByte, &texelsPtr, 0));
868
869 gl::PixelPackState packState;
870 packState.alignment = 1;
871
872 ANGLE_TRY(texture->getTexImage(context, packState, nullptr, index.getTarget(),
873 index.getLevelIndex(), getFormat, getType,
874 texelsPtr->data()));
875 bos->writeBytes(texelsPtr->data(), texelsPtr->size());
876 }
877 return Result::Continue;
878}
879
880Result SerializeTexture(const gl::Context *context,
881 gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
882 ScratchBuffer *scratchBuffer,
883 gl::Texture *texture)
884{
885 SerializeTextureState(bos, texture->getState());
886 bos->writeString(texture->getLabel());
887 // FrameCapture can not serialize mBoundSurface and mBoundStream
888 // because they are likely to change with each run
889 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeTextureData(bos, context, texture, scratchBuffer));
890 return Result::Continue;
891}

898void SerializeVertexAttributeVector(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
899 const std::vector<gl::VertexAttribute> &vertexAttributes)
900{
901 for (const gl::VertexAttribute &vertexAttribute : vertexAttributes)
902 {
903 bos->writeBool(vertexAttribute.enabled);
904 ASSERT(vertexAttribute.format);
905 SerializeFormat(bos, vertexAttribute.format);
906 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribute.relativeOffset);
907 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribute.vertexAttribArrayStride);
908 bos->writeInt(vertexAttribute.bindingIndex);
909 }
910}

912void SerializeVertexBindingsVector(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
913 const std::vector<gl::VertexBinding> &vertexBindings)
914{
915 for (const gl::VertexBinding &vertexBinding : vertexBindings)
916 {
917 bos->writeInt(vertexBinding.getStride());
918 bos->writeInt(vertexBinding.getDivisor());
919 bos->writeInt(vertexBinding.getOffset());
920 bos->writeInt(vertexBinding.getBuffer().id().value);
921 bos->writeInt(vertexBinding.getBoundAttributesMask().to_ulong());
922 }
923}

925void SerializeVertexArrayState(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos,
926 const gl::VertexArrayState &vertexArrayState)
927{
928 bos->writeString(vertexArrayState.getLabel());
929 SerializeVertexAttributeVector(bos, vertexArrayState.getVertexAttributes());
930 if (vertexArrayState.getElementArrayBuffer())
931 {
932 bos->writeInt(vertexArrayState.getElementArrayBuffer()->id().value);
933 }
934 else
935 {
936 bos->writeInt(0);
937 }
938 SerializeVertexBindingsVector(bos, vertexArrayState.getVertexBindings());
939 bos->writeInt(vertexArrayState.getEnabledAttributesMask().to_ulong());
940 bos->writeInt(vertexArrayState.getVertexAttributesTypeMask().to_ulong());
941 bos->writeInt(vertexArrayState.getClientMemoryAttribsMask().to_ulong());
942 bos->writeInt(vertexArrayState.getNullPointerClientMemoryAttribsMask().to_ulong());
943}

945void SerializeVertexArray(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, gl::VertexArray *vertexArray)
946{
947 bos->writeInt(vertexArray->id().value);
948 SerializeVertexArrayState(bos, vertexArray->getState());
949 bos->writeBool(vertexArray->isBufferAccessValidationEnabled());
950}

954Result SerializeContext(gl::BinaryOutputStream *bos, const gl::Context *context)
955{
956 SerializeGLContextStates(bos, context->getState());
957 ScratchBuffer scratchBuffer(1);
958 const gl::FramebufferManager &framebufferManager =
959 context->getState().getFramebufferManagerForCapture();
960 for (const auto &framebuffer : framebufferManager)
961 {
962 gl::Framebuffer *framebufferPtr = framebuffer.second;
963 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeFramebuffer(context, bos, &scratchBuffer, framebufferPtr));
964 }
965 const gl::BufferManager &bufferManager = context->getState().getBufferManagerForCapture();
966 for (const auto &buffer : bufferManager)
967 {
968 gl::Buffer *bufferPtr = buffer.second;
969 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeBuffer(context, bos, &scratchBuffer, bufferPtr));
970 }
971 const gl::SamplerManager &samplerManager = context->getState().getSamplerManagerForCapture();
972 for (const auto &sampler : samplerManager)
973 {
974 gl::Sampler *samplerPtr = sampler.second;
975 SerializeSampler(bos, samplerPtr);
976 }
977 const gl::RenderbufferManager &renderbufferManager =
978 context->getState().getRenderbufferManagerForCapture();
979 for (const auto &renderbuffer : renderbufferManager)
980 {
981 gl::Renderbuffer *renderbufferPtr = renderbuffer.second;
982 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeRenderbuffer(context, bos, &scratchBuffer, renderbufferPtr));
983 }
984 const gl::ShaderProgramManager &shaderProgramManager =
985 context->getState().getShaderProgramManagerForCapture();
986 const gl::ResourceMap<gl::Shader, gl::ShaderProgramID> &shaderManager =
987 shaderProgramManager.getShadersForCapture();
988 for (const auto &shader : shaderManager)
989 {
990 gl::Shader *shaderPtr = shader.second;
991 SerializeShader(bos, shaderPtr);
992 }
993 const gl::ResourceMap<gl::Program, gl::ShaderProgramID> &programManager =
994 shaderProgramManager.getProgramsForCaptureAndPerf();
995 for (const auto &program : programManager)
996 {
997 gl::Program *programPtr = program.second;
998 SerializeProgram(bos, programPtr);
999 }
1000 const gl::TextureManager &textureManager = context->getState().getTextureManagerForCapture();
1001 for (const auto &texture : textureManager)
1002 {
1003 gl::Texture *texturePtr = texture.second;
1004 ANGLE_TRY(SerializeTexture(context, bos, &scratchBuffer, texturePtr));
1005 }
1006 const gl::VertexArrayMap &vertexArrayMap = context->getVertexArraysForCapture();
1007 for (auto &vertexArray : vertexArrayMap)
1008 {
1009 gl::VertexArray *vertexArrayPtr = vertexArray.second;
1010 SerializeVertexArray(bos, vertexArrayPtr);
1011 }
1012
1013 scratchBuffer.clear();
1014 return Result::Continue;
1015}
